            },
            {
              "inputArgName": "subject",
              "inputArgValue": "<p>Nuova richiesta preventivo - <span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.company\" data-label=\"$form.company\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.company }}</span> <span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.email\" data-label=\"$form.email\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.email }}</span></p>"
            },
            {
              "inputArgName": "body",
              "inputArgValue": "<p>Nuova richiesta preventivo ricevuta dalla demo Mail Automation.</p><p>Google Sheet lead: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1m0cy4el1lM2c5JQaoD3w4P7ukWWK-XfASWevqTUC5YA/edit\">apri il foglio</a></p><p>In allegato trovi il file Excel con i dati del lead.</p><p><strong>Nome:</strong> <span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.name\" data-label=\"$form.name\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.name }}</span><br><strong>Email:</strong> <span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.email\" data-label=\"$form.email\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.email }}</span><br><strong>Azienda:</strong> <span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.company\" data-label=\"$form.company\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.company }}</span><br><strong>Uso demo:</strong> <span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.usedRuns\" data-label=\"$form.usedRuns\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.usedRuns }}</span>/<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.maxRuns\" data-label=\"$form.maxRuns\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.maxRuns }}</span> invii.</p>"
            },
            {
              "inputArgName": "attachmentFilename",
              "inputArgValue": "<p>lead-preventivo.xls</p>"
            },
            {
              "inputArgName": "attachmentMimeType",
              "inputArgValue": "<p>application/vnd.ms-excel</p>"
            },
            {
              "inputArgName": "attachmentContent",
              "inputArgValue": "<p><table border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>Data richiesta</th><th>Nome</th><th>Email</th><th>Azienda</th><th>Sito web</th><th>Ruolo</th><th>Obiettivo</th><th>Invii usati</th><th>Invii rimasti</th><th>Invii massimi</th><th>Lead ID</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.quoteRequestedAt\" data-label=\"$form.quoteRequestedAt\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.quoteRequestedAt }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.name\" data-label=\"$form.name\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.name }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.email\" data-label=\"$form.email\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.email }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.company\" data-label=\"$form.company\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.company }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.website\" data-label=\"$form.website\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.website }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.role\" data-label=\"$form.role\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.role }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.useCase\" data-label=\"$form.useCase\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.useCase }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.usedRuns\" data-label=\"$form.usedRuns\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.usedRuns }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.remainingRuns\" data-label=\"$form.remainingRuns\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.remainingRuns }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.maxRuns\" data-label=\"$form.maxRuns\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.maxRuns }}</span></td><td><span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.leadId\" data-label=\"$form.leadId\" data-mention-suggestion-char=\"@\">{{ $form.leadId }}</span></td></tr></tbody></table></p>"
            }
